    <p>LaToya C. Davis is the Co-Founder of Abundant Faith Fellowship Church, and First Assistant to her husband, Pastor W. Trey Davis. Lady "D" currently holds a Bachelors of Science Degree in Child Development from Texas Southern University, as well as a Masters of Education in Advanced Literacy from Concordia University. Her future plans are to pursue her Doctorate in Education, as well as serve as Executive Director of Abundant Faith Fellowship Academy.</p>
